item.title: Understanding RAML
item.dc:creator: Srivatsan Sundararajan
item.description:
What is RAML?RAML stands for RESTful API Modeling Language. It is a YAML based language for defining RESTful APIs and contains all the necessary information to describe RESTful APIs. YAML is a data serialization language that is easier to read and understand than other formats like XML or JSON.More details on RAML and its usage […]
